= sfTarBallPlugin - A simple pake task to package you project in a tarball =

== Author ==

Alon Noy, [http://www.frames4technology.nl/]

== Overview ==

A simple task that make the sequence of 'symfony freeze', 'tar -czf ...' and 'symfony unfreeze' all in one call.

== License ==

For the full copyright and license information, please view the LICENSE
file that was distributed with this source code.

== Installation ==

To install the plugin use `symfony plugin-install` command

== Using the plugin ==

Just do 'symfony tar' and your project tarball will be created one directory level higher then your project directory root, ready to be deployed.

